company.name: ASIAC
company.description:
ASIAC supports adoption for children in need of families, and is committed to developing community awareness of overseas adoption.

We aim to: 

encourage and facilitate intercountry adoption 
support, guide and educate its members during all stages of the adoption journey 
advocate for and support children in need in overseas countries through education and funding projects.
